a combination of the void and the solid,

37
00:02:10,140 --> 00:02:11,380
and spot arrangements.

38
00:02:11,740 --> 00:02:14,100
The negative space is necessary
to create a sense of artistry.

39
00:02:14,860 --> 00:02:16,140
Just looking

40
00:02:16,340 --> 00:02:17,620
at this dish's plating,

41
00:02:17,620 --> 00:02:18,820
it's obvious

42
00:02:19,540 --> 00:02:22,540
that the chef lacks

43
00:02:23,100 --> 00:02:24,820
professional training.

44
00:02:25,580 --> 00:02:27,140
Finally, someone gets it.

45
00:02:27,780 --> 00:02:29,420
Yin Miaolan truly deserves her title

46
00:02:29,420 --> 00:02:31,620
as an international
culinary consultant indeed.

47
00:02:31,940 --> 00:02:33,540
A remarkable consultant indeed.

48
00:02:33,820 --> 00:02:35,340
But a couple of days ago,

49
00:02:35,480 --> 00:02:36,940
I saw her visiting Hua Su.

50
00:02:38,860 --> 00:02:41,860
As the judges here,

51
00:02:42,140 --> 00:02:43,500
you should uphold their professionalism

52
00:02:43,780 --> 00:02:45,900
and maintain culinary standards

53
00:02:46,140 --> 00:02:47,900
during the assessment.

54
00:02:52,740 --> 00:02:53,740
So,

55
00:02:53,740 --> 00:02:55,780
as the culinary consultant

56
00:02:55,780 --> 00:02:57,060
and head judge for this competition,

57
00:02:58,700 --> 00:03:00,140
I don't agree

58
00:03:00,140 --> 00:03:01,660
with Hua Su's entry into the finals.

59
00:03:07,070 --> 00:03:08,010
Is there any reason for this?

60
00:03:39,060 --> 00:03:39,900
Brother Xie Jun,

61
00:03:39,940 --> 00:03:41,140
go comfort her.

62
00:03:41,140 --> 00:03:42,140
You're her childhood friend.

63
00:03:42,140 --> 00:03:42,980
I…

64
00:03:43,620 --> 00:03:44,540
I wouldn't dare.

65
00:03:45,420 --> 00:03:47,500
Gao Ying, you are her best friend.

66
00:03:47,780 --> 00:03:49,220
- You do it.
- Me…

67
00:03:50,300 --> 00:03:51,380
Me neither.

68
00:03:51,380 --> 00:03:53,220
I don't dare provoke her now.

69
00:03:57,420 --> 00:03:58,340
I'll do it.

70
00:03:58,900 --> 00:04:00,420
We're close.

71
00:04:01,420 --> 00:04:02,340
I understand her.

72
00:04:05,740 --> 00:04:06,580
Meng.

73
00:04:06,780 --> 00:04:07,620
Get lost.

74
00:04:12,900 --> 00:04:13,820
I don't understand her.

75
00:04:30,900 --> 00:04:31,860
Do you know

76
00:04:32,660 --> 00:04:34,860
that the judge who eliminated me today

77
00:04:35,540 --> 00:04:37,020
was actually my mom?

78
00:04:43,540 --> 00:04:45,300
Why aren't you surprised?

79
00:04:45,780 --> 00:04:47,300
Wasn't she invited by you?

80
00:04:49,100 --> 00:04:50,060
What a coincidence.

81
00:04:53,180 --> 00:04:54,660
I wouldn't have attended

82
00:04:56,660 --> 00:04:57,820
if I had known she was one of judges.

83
00:04:59,900 --> 00:05:01,980
Actually, she came to Hua Su,

84
00:05:02,460 --> 00:05:04,380
and asked me to study abroad,

85
00:05:06,660 --> 00:05:08,020
but only

86
00:05:11,860 --> 00:05:13,340
if I abandoned Hua Su.

87
00:05:14,260 --> 00:05:15,460
Is it an either/or proposition?

88
00:05:16,340 --> 00:05:18,740
She disapproves of my Dad's philosophy.

89
00:05:20,620 --> 00:05:21,980
That's why

90
00:05:23,340 --> 00:05:25,060
they separated.

91
00:05:43,700 --> 00:05:45,660
I may have to give up Hua Su.

92
00:05:48,980 --> 00:05:51,660
I can't protect it anymore.

93
00:06:17,580 --> 00:06:18,420
Thank you.

94
00:06:19,580 --> 00:06:20,540
With all due respect,

95
00:06:21,300 --> 00:06:23,180
the issues between you and Master Pi

96
00:06:23,620 --> 00:06:25,420
should not affect your daughter.

97
00:06:31,020 --> 00:06:32,060
Looks like

98
00:06:32,980 --> 00:06:35,660
you've done your homework, Mr. Shu,

99
00:06:36,100 --> 00:06:37,300
and are even digging up

100
00:06:37,300 --> 00:06:38,540
my old stories.

101
00:06:39,380 --> 00:06:40,420
I just didn't expect

102
00:06:41,020 --> 00:06:41,940
you'd let

103
00:06:41,940 --> 00:06:43,660
emotions interfere

104
00:06:44,020 --> 00:06:44,950
with professional judgment.

105
00:06:46,140 --> 00:06:47,460
I'm not emotional.

106
00:06:48,740 --> 00:06:50,300
As Hua Su's new owner,

107
00:06:51,180 --> 00:06:52,140
she must

108
00:06:52,140 --> 00:06:53,580
create her style.

109
00:06:54,020 --> 00:06:55,420
Her dishes now

110
00:06:55,660 --> 00:06:57,060
only reflect Pi Zijie's style.

111
00:06:57,060 --> 00:06:59,340
I see nothing uniquely hers.

112
00:07:02,580 --> 00:07:03,420
Then tell me,

113
00:07:03,500 --> 00:07:04,740
how can I evaluate that dish?

114
00:07:05,700 --> 00:07:07,100
Even if I taste

115
00:07:07,100 --> 00:07:08,500
and score it,

116
00:07:08,500 --> 00:07:09,780
the credit goes to Pi Zijie,

117
00:07:09,780 --> 00:07:10,860
not Fang Meng.

118
00:07:12,300 --> 00:07:13,740
Don't your Bo Fei Group

119
00:07:13,740 --> 00:07:15,460
want to introduce Hua Su

120
00:07:15,460 --> 00:07:16,450
with Fang Meng as the head chef,

121
00:07:17,060 --> 00:07:18,460
not Pi Zijie?

122
00:07:19,700 --> 00:07:20,980
I know her well.

123
00:07:21,820 --> 00:07:23,780
She wants Fang Meng to give up Hua Su

124
00:07:23,780 --> 00:07:25,020
and study her philosophy abroad.

125
00:07:30,580 --> 00:07:31,900
So you're saying

126
00:07:32,820 --> 00:07:35,140
Fang Meng is copying Master Pi's dishes,

127
00:07:35,280 --> 00:07:36,260
and that's why you won't try them.

128
00:07:36,980 --> 00:07:38,700
If Fang Meng creates her own dish,

129
00:07:39,260 --> 00:07:40,660
would you taste

130
00:07:40,900 --> 00:07:42,980
and score it?

131
00:07:48,700 --> 00:07:49,540
Ms. Yin,

132
00:07:50,460 --> 00:07:51,540
Fang Meng told me

133
00:07:52,060 --> 00:07:53,260
you want her to study abroad.

134
00:07:54,060 --> 00:07:55,580
If she has regrets,

135
00:07:56,300 --> 00:07:57,940
I think she won't go with you.

136
00:07:59,460 --> 00:08:01,420
So I'm asking you to give her a chance

137
00:08:02,180 --> 00:08:03,820
to taste her dish.

138
00:08:04,500 --> 00:08:05,540
If she fails,

139
00:08:06,020 --> 00:08:08,060
she'll go with you willingly.

140
00:08:08,740 --> 00:08:09,860
If she succeeds,

141
00:08:10,580 --> 00:08:11,500
wouldn't it be a win

142
00:08:11,740 --> 00:08:13,020
for you too?

143
00:08:20,620 --> 00:08:21,780
I don't want to go.

144
00:08:23,060 --> 00:08:23,980
Why not?

145
00:08:24,180 --> 00:08:25,460
I've already convinced your mother.

146
00:08:26,580 --> 00:08:27,780
I have already convinced Yin Miaolan

147
00:08:27,780 --> 00:08:28,900
to let you enter the finals.

148
00:08:32,540 --> 00:08:34,100
I don't need her pity.

149
00:08:35,220 --> 00:08:37,020
This isn't the first time I've lost

150
00:08:37,260 --> 00:08:39,620
or the first time someone said
I'm bad at cooking.

151
00:08:40,420 --> 00:08:41,580
Let's not do it,

152
00:08:42,100 --> 00:08:42,940
okay?

153
00:08:47,100 --> 00:08:48,300
You're giving up now?

154
00:08:48,540 --> 00:08:49,740
Think about Hua Su,

155
00:08:49,740 --> 00:08:50,740
think about Master Pi,

156
00:08:50,900 --> 00:08:51,820
think about me,

157
00:08:52,220 --> 00:08:53,100
and Xie Jun, Shen An'an

158
00:08:53,100 --> 00:08:54,340
Gao Ying, Dazui,

159
00:08:54,540 --> 00:08:55,500
and other friends

160
00:08:55,500 --> 00:08:56,660
cheering for you.

161
00:08:56,860 --> 00:08:59,180
They're there not just
because they're your friends

162
00:08:59,180 --> 00:09:00,100
to cheer you on

163
00:09:00,100 --> 00:09:01,340
but because they believe in you.

164
00:09:01,500 --> 00:09:03,060
We believe in you. Do you understand?

165
00:09:03,380 --> 00:09:05,020
You can't be defeated by others,

166
00:09:05,500 --> 00:09:08,100
and you definitely can't be defeated
by yourself.

167
00:09:18,180 --> 00:09:19,020
Tomorrow morning,

168
00:09:19,340 --> 00:09:20,660
I will wait for you at the finals.

