I've been preparing ingredients
all morning.

180
00:10:09,420 --> 00:10:10,660
Why don't you come to help?

181
00:10:17,860 --> 00:10:19,860
Alright, dear audience,

182
00:10:19,860 --> 00:10:20,820
I now declare

183
00:10:20,820 --> 00:10:22,580
the SAGA Food Street

184
