190
00:10:32,740 --> 00:10:36,020
He specializes in Huaiyang Cuisine
and Cantonese Cuisine

191
00:10:36,020 --> 00:10:39,980
and is a three-time champion
of Yucheng Culinary Competition.

192
00:10:48,180 --> 00:10:49,260
Look at you, come over here.

193
00:10:53,140 --> 00:10:54,260
Next,

194
00:10:54,700 --> 00:10:57,460
we have Li Dalong,
head chef of Liuliuniu Restaurant.

195
00:10:59,180 --> 00:11:00,620
Yeah.

196
00:11:02,500 --> 00:11:03,980
Li Dalong won first prize

197
00:11:03,980 --> 00:11:06,740
in the national dessert competition

198
00:11:06,740 --> 00:11:09,740
with his desert
called Grandma Liu's Durian Milk.

199
00:11:11,260 --> 00:11:12,980
In addition, he has led

200
00:11:12,980 --> 00:11:14,100
Liuliuniu Restaurant to be

201
00:11:14,100 --> 00:11:15,500
the nation's most popular restaurant

202
00:11:15,500 --> 00:11:17,740
for two years in a row.

203
00:11:18,980 --> 00:11:19,860
The third

204
00:11:19,860 --> 00:11:23,500
is Simon,

205
00:11:23,500 --> 00:11:24,500
(Simon, Head Chef)
head chef of MIX Restaurant.

206
00:11:25,500 --> 00:11:27,160
As a chef with mixed heritage
from eight countries,

207
00:11:27,160 --> 00:11:28,540
Simon combines

208
00:11:28,700 --> 00:11:31,900
international techniques

209
00:11:31,900 --> 00:11:35,860
and is renowned for his cutting skills.

210
00:11:41,460 --> 00:11:42,580
You have your own strengths.

211
00:11:43,020 --> 00:11:43,900
Don't worry.

212
00:11:49,960 --> 00:11:50,820
And finally, our dark house,

213
00:11:50,820 --> 00:11:52,980
stunning in the preliminaries,

214
00:11:53,140 --> 00:11:54,180
eliminated in the semis,

215
00:11:54,180 --> 00:11:56,100
and revived for the finals,

216
00:11:56,460 --> 00:11:58,740
Fang Meng from Hua Su Restaurant!

217
00:11:59,740 --> 00:12:01,820
(Fang Meng)

218
00:12:02,580 --> 00:12:03,420
Meng,

219
00:12:03,980 --> 00:12:05,460
I've stuck with you till the end.

220
00:12:06,140 --> 00:12:06,980
Go get them!

221
00:12:09,140 --> 00:12:09,980
Go get them!

222
00:12:18,580 --> 00:12:19,860
I've heard

223
00:12:19,860 --> 00:12:21,820
these chefs are all hidden masters.

224
00:12:25,660 --> 00:12:26,700
Truly impressive.

225
00:12:27,220 --> 00:12:28,980
So fast that I can't even see the knife.

226
00:12:41,980 --> 00:12:43,180
Yet you even show off.

227
00:12:50,540 --> 00:12:51,380
Oh my!

228
00:12:52,780 --> 00:12:53,620
Dazui!

229
00:12:53,900 --> 00:12:55,100
Are you blind?

230
00:12:55,340 --> 00:12:57,540
Why are you showing off
when you can't do it?

231
00:12:58,820 --> 00:12:59,660
Dazui!

232
00:13:02,420 --> 00:13:04,020
Sir, you're under suspicion
for attempted murder.

233
00:13:04,020 --> 00:13:04,860
You'll come with us.

234
00:13:17,180 --> 00:13:19,700
Alright, there's been a minor accident.

235
00:13:19,700 --> 00:13:21,380
Now, I announce that today's competition

236
00:13:21,380 --> 00:13:22,980
will directly proceed

237
00:13:23,140 --> 00:13:24,860
to the championship match!

238
00:13:25,540 --> 00:13:26,780
Alright, let me

239
00:13:26,780 --> 00:13:28,340
explain the rules.

240
00:13:28,340 --> 00:13:30,420
This is a no-theme competition today.

241
00:13:30,900 --> 00:13:33,660
Each chef has only one chance
to make a dish.

242
00:13:33,660 --> 00:13:35,500
The high score wins.

243
00:13:35,500 --> 00:13:36,660
Alright, without further ado,

244
00:13:36,660 --> 00:13:39,900
let's begin the competition.

245
00:14:02,220 --> 00:14:03,620
This is not my ingredient bag.

246
00:14:09,780 --> 00:14:10,660
Miss Fang,

247
00:14:11,740 --> 00:14:13,220
please don't blame me.

248
00:14:14,300 --> 00:14:16,220
Blame Shu Zhengyan instead.

249
00:14:21,700 --> 00:14:24,020
Sir, my ingredient bag has been switched.

250
00:14:25,220 --> 00:14:28,060
I'm afraid I can't help you with that.

251
00:14:28,060 --> 00:14:29,500
But these are all just some

252
00:14:29,500 --> 00:14:30,860
leftovers from others.

253
00:14:31,100 --> 00:14:33,380
The ingredients were prepared
by the contestants themselves.

254
00:14:33,660 --> 00:14:35,140
So, managing them is your responsibility.

255
00:15:02,340 --> 00:15:03,180
Fang Meng,

256
00:15:04,700 --> 00:15:05,900
why are you back?

257
00:15:05,900 --> 00:15:06,740
How is Big Mouth?

258
00:15:06,900 --> 00:15:08,420
He's fine. Don't worry.

259
00:15:10,340 --> 00:15:11,180
Fang Meng,

260
00:15:12,100 --> 00:15:12,940
Dazui is okay.

261
00:15:14,460 --> 00:15:15,820
- Meng.
- Don't push yourself too hard.

262
00:15:16,020 --> 00:15:16,900
This time,

263
00:15:17,180 --> 00:15:18,460
I can't help you.

264
00:15:19,060 --> 00:15:20,420
As long as you're okay.

265
00:15:21,380 --> 00:15:22,220
I'm fine.

266
00:15:22,540 --> 00:15:23,620
I'm here to cheer you on.

267
00:15:25,140 --> 00:15:25,980
Keep going.

268
00:15:26,020 --> 00:15:27,140
- Keep going.
- We'll go ahead first.

269
00:15:37,580 --> 00:15:38,420
I'll stay with you.

270
00:15:43,380 --> 00:15:44,220
We'll face this together.

271
00:15:56,700 --> 00:15:58,980
Mr. Shu, your direct involvement might…

272
00:15:58,980 --> 00:16:00,900
I won't cook or speak.

273
00:16:01,340 --> 00:16:02,260
I'll just stand with her,

274
00:16:02,940 --> 00:16:03,780
like everyone else.

275
00:16:07,740 --> 00:16:08,900
The sixth dish!

276
00:16:09,380 --> 00:16:10,220
Quick, have a taste.

277
00:16:10,540 --> 00:16:13,060
There's nothing on the recipe
for this dish.

278
00:16:13,980 --> 00:16:15,780
You've always guided me before.

279
00:16:16,220 --> 00:16:17,940
Do you have any idea this time?

280
00:16:18,620 --> 00:16:20,380
The first five dishes alone

281
00:16:20,540 --> 00:16:22,660
won't make you a true chef.

282
00:16:23,140 --> 00:16:25,540
You need to create something
unique to you.

283
00:16:41,220 --> 00:16:43,780
(Food Street Culinary Competition Finals)

284
00:17:36,980 --> 00:17:40,540
People in Jiangnan value
eating with the seasons.

285
00:17:41,420 --> 00:17:43,140
This dish

286
00:17:43,140 --> 00:17:45,140
